      "evidence": [
        "`urbitContainerConfWithRuntime` loads `shipConf` up front, invokes `UpdateUrbitFn(shipConf)` (which can persist updates), and later calls `LoadUrbitConfigFn` but continues subsequent `shipConf`-based decisions from the pre-update object.",
